item.title: 【Interviews / TV shows / Others】HDTV - Lady GAGA ONLY Edit - Interview Graham Norton Show S29E08 1080p
item.description:
Here is a big project edited by me. Edited together all the shots of Lady Gaga from her appearance on The Graham Norton Show season 29 episode 8. Lots of editing went into this; I had to manually crop and zoom-in the far away shots in addition to separating each individual shot of Gaga. This can be used to make GIFs with or to watch only the Gaga parts without interruption from the other guests or host. Original video length was 47:32. Edited down to only Gaga shots is now 11:03. After making almost exclusively Katy Perry posts I figured it was time to start making Gaga videos, especially given my username.
